{#
  Step 3: Upload a meeting recording
  - Click "New meeting" then "Upload a file"
  - Choose or drag an audio file (MP3, WAV, or WebM)
  - Select a template (General is the default)
  - Click "Upload"
  - See "Transcription being processed"
#}

